### 1. Software Description

Acuspic is an Android Markdown editor with the following features:
- Support for 6 Markdown dialects: GFM, CommonMark, Original, MultiMarkdown, Markdown Extra, Pandoc
- Integration with 6 image hosting services: Gitee, GitHub, Qiniu, SM.MS, Imgur, Custom
- Local data storage, core features work offline
- Dual-source update system (GitHub/Gitee)

---

